query:
SELECT 
  i.id as inventoryId,
  i.productId,
  p.sku,
  p.description,
  i.quantity,
  i.reservedQuantity,
  (i.quantity - i.reservedQuantity) as available,
  wl.code as locationCode,
  wz.code as zoneCode,
  wz.name as zoneName
FROM inventory i
JOIN products p ON p.id = i.productId
JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON wl.id = i.locationId
JOIN warehouseZones wz ON wz.id = wl.zoneId
WHERE i.productId IN (
  SELECT poi.productId
  FROM pickingOrderItems poi
  WHERE poi.pickingOrderId IN (
    SELECT smi.pickingOrderId 
    FROM shipmentManifests sm
    JOIN shipmentManifestItems smi ON smi.manifestId = sm.id
    WHERE sm.manifestNumber = 'ROM-1769734935811'
  )
)
AND wz.code = 'EXP'
AND i.status = 'available';
